n amounts on your invoices, debit notes, and credit notes separately.","pos":[12159,12270]},{"content":"Therefore, you map the various reporting codes (1001 for invoices, 1002 for debit notes, and 1003 for credit notes) to specific tax codes.","pos":[12271,12409]},{"content":"Meanwhile, if you must display, for example, Total Value of Standard Rated Supply in GST-03, credit notes, debit notes, and invoices aren't differentiated.","pos":[12410,12565]},{"content":"Therefore, you must select <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>1001<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>1002<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>, and <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>1003<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> for the transaction amounts.","pos":[12566,12654],"source":" Therefore, you must select **1001**, **1002**, and **1003** for the transaction amounts."},{"pos":[12660,12706],"content":"Running the GST report by configuration report","linkify":"Running the GST report by configuration report","nodes":[{"content":"Running the GST report by configuration report","pos":[0,46]}]},{"content":"After you book your transactions and define your report configurations, you can run the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>GST report by configuration<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> report.","pos":[12708,12835],"source":"After you book your transactions and define your report configurations, you can run the **GST report by configuration** report."},{"content":"You must provide following parameters:","pos":[12836,12874]},{"pos":[12880,12960],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Settlement period:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> Specify the settlement period to generate the report for.","source":"**Settlement period:** Specify the settlement period to generate the report for."},{"pos":[12965,13038],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>From date:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> The first date in the interval for this settlement period.","source":"**From date:** The first date in the interval for this settlement period."},{"pos":[13043,13129],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Report configura