charges are regarded as \"purchases\" in GAF.","pos":[14244,14360]},{"content":"In such cases, Dynamics 365 for Operations allows users to capture the required GAF information.","pos":[14362,14458]},{"content":"You are now able to capture \"Organization number\" for a bank group.","pos":[14459,14526]},{"content":"It will be defaulted to payment fee transactions of corresponding banks.","pos":[14527,14599]},{"content":"And you can enter required GAF information for various journals and payment fees as per your business needs.","pos":[14600,14708]},{"content":"You also can preview the supply and purchase records where GST applies and you can edit or add relevant information in the \"GAF purchase and supply review\" page.","pos":[14710,14871]},{"content":"You need make sure you mark the \"GST\" check box on the Sales tax codes page for each of your GST tax codes.","pos":[14873,14980]},{"content":"To generate the GAF, click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Tax<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> <ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;gt;</ph> <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Declarations<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> <ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;gt;</ph> <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Sales tax<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> <ph id=\"ph3\">&amp;gt;</ph> <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>Generate GAF file<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept>, and provide the following required information:","pos":[14981,15132],"source":" To generate the GAF, click **Tax** &gt; **Declarations** &gt; **Sales tax** &gt; **Generate GAF file**, and provide the following required information:"},{"pos":[15138,15215],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Settlement period:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> Specify the settlement period to generate the GAF for.","source":"**Settlement period:** Specify the settlement period to generate the GAF for."},{"pos":[15220,15293],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>From date:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> The first date in the interval for this settlement period.","source":"**From date:** The first date in the interval for this settlement period."},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Creation date:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> The GAF creation date.","pos":[15298,15339],"source":"**Creation date:** The GAF creation date."},{"content":"This information will appear in the company section of the GAF.","pos":[15340,15403]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Posting layer:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> Specify which posting layers to generate the GAF from.","pos":[15408,15481],"source":"**Posting layer:** Specify which posting layers to generate the GAF from."},{"content":"The posting layers affect the ledger transactions that are included in the GAF.","pos":[15482,15561]},{"content":"You should run the “Settle and post sales tax” process before you generate the GAF for a period.","pos":[15563,15659]},{"content":"Only those transactions that are included in a sales tax payment will be included in the GAF.","pos":[15660,15753]}]}